item.title: A Sentiment Analysis of Child Language Acquisition Data
item.description: Join us for a night of four talks from students in OHSU’s Principles and Practice of Data Visualization, taught by Alison Hill, Steve Bedrick, and Jackie Wirz (https://github.com/apreshill/data-vis-labs-2018 | https://apreshill.github.io/data-vis-labs-2018/). Speakers: Alex Salem: A Sentimental Analysis of Tolstoy Grace Lawley: A Sentiment Analysis of Child Language Acquisition Data Ryan Opel: Sole Mates: Analysis of Nike’s BIKETOWN Sneaker Bikes Alexandra Michel: Winning at Twitter with ggplot: What’s Up With Colorado Basin Water Use?
